# Hire Ready AI 🚀

An AI-powered resume analyzer and interview simulator.

## Features
- Resume Analysis using AI
- Suggested Job Roles
- AI-based Interview Simulation
- Real-time Feedback & Scoring

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React (Styled Components)
- Backend: FastAPI (Python)
- Deployment: Render

